Guitar Masters 12 of 16 A Tablatures Collection by cipolloide

Still today people ask me about the old guitar torrents that I shared years ago at my first times at the Bay.
They often tell me that is difficult to find them all, cause the TPB search engine sucks, cause their trackers are dead and they seem deserted.
So I've decided to reshare them all with a unifying pattern in the name of the torrent:

Guitar Masters

followed by a progressive number, so those who are interested can find them easily.
They deal primarily with fingerstyle, and the albums they contain are not generally easy to find... so dont expect overall 320 bitrates.
The founding criterion here is to find and remember them as a document of great music of the past.

Enjoy :)

A collection of fingerstyle guitar transcriptions made with Guitar Pro
Most of the tunes tabbed are available in mp3 format in the previous torrents of my Guitar Masters collection. The degree of difficulty varies greatly: from simple tunes easy to pick up and play to real finger breaking tour de force :)

They're not organized as a method since they were only tunes that greatly intrigued me and that I wanted to practise. Some come from books, some from transcription of mine, some from transcription of others.

I hope you dig and enjoy them for long hours as I did myself with them :)
